        <item>
            <title>英製雙層電巴投入服務，九巴：成本貴柴油巴逾半冀能獲政府資助</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/11/adlbus/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=adlbus</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/11/adlbus/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 09:01:23 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[亞歷山大丹尼士]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[電巴]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1235110</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前來自英國巴士製造商亞歷山大丹尼士（ADL）的 Enviro500EV 雙層電巴通過運輸署測試，並獲發牌。首輛專為香港設計的全新 Enviro500EV，今日在城巴 112 號線，從長沙灣蘇屋邨至北角百福道間運行，吸引了大量巴士迷及市民體驗。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235116" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413468230-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413468230-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413468230.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>該款電巴在中國大陸組裝，主要零件來自歐洲，採用 ADL 電池，這些電巴搭載水冷系統和電池管理系統，並在車頂裝設了太陽能薄膜，增強了電池的效能和壽命。電巴充電時間約 2.5 小時，續航力可達 300 公里，足以應對大部分日常路線的需求。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235111" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413306452-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413306452-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413306452.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Enviro500EV 電巴設計亦考慮到乘客的舒適和安全，車內裝有仿木地板和大地色系座椅，提供雙輪椅泊位、免費 5G WiFi 和 USB 充電插座等設施。與比亞迪電巴相比，ADL 電池的配置令下層可配置更多座位，達到 27 個。</p><p>首次運行的 Enviro500EV 雙層電巴吸引大批市民試乘，當中包括不少巴士迷。早上 9 點已有人在長沙灣排隊，巴士迷對這次新車的首航表現感到滿意，尤其是其平穩的剎車和加速性能，以及比較安靜的駕駛環境。九巴已計劃將這款電巴投入更多過海路線，進一步擴展其電動車隊，實現 2040 年全線轉向新能源車的目標。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235112" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413394288-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413394288-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413394288.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235113" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413407833-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413407833-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413407833.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235115" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413424066-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413424066-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413424066.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p>九巴傳訊及公共事務部主管簡學悕表示，電巴成本較傳統柴油巴士高出一半。未來希望能獲得政府的資助。早前九巴行政總監（署理）關翠蘭曾表示，公司正與政府商討資助事宜，並強調不會依賴單一車廠，以分散投資風險，但暫未決定 ADL 與比亞迪電巴的比例。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235114" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413477784-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413477784-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413477784.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20240511/s00001/1715412705287/%e8%8b%b1%e8%a3%bd%e9%9b%99%e5%b1%a4%e9%9b%bb%e5%b7%b4%e4%bb%8a%e9%a6%96%e8%bc%89%e5%ae%a2-%e9%80%be%e7%99%be%e3%80%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%a3%ab%e8%bf%b7%e3%80%8d%e7%ad%89%e5%80%99-%e6%88%90%e6%9c%ac%e8%bc%83%e6%9f%b4%e6%b2%b9%e5%b7%b4%e8%b2%b4%e9%80%be%e5%8d%8a-%e4%b9%9d%e5%b7%b4%e7%9b%bc%e7%8d%b2%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e8%b3%87%e5%8a%a9">明報</a>、<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20231104/s00001/1699028032272/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A510%E8%BC%9B%E8%8B%B1%E8%A3%BD%E9%9B%99%E5%B1%A4%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB-%E5%8F%AF%E8%BC%89%E5%AE%A2127%E4%BA%BA-%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E7%BD%B2%E6%AD%A3%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6">明報</a>、<a href="https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/996207/%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E8%8B%B1%E8%A3%BD%E9%9B%99%E5%B1%A4%E9%9B%BB%E5%B7%B4-%E8%BC%89%E5%AE%A2%E9%87%8F122%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E4%B9%8B%E5%86%A0-%E5%B0%87%E8%A1%8C%E9%A7%9B%E9%81%8E%E6%B5%B7%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A">香港 01</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.kmb.hk/news_detail.html?id=908&amp;year=2024">九巴</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/11/adlbus/life-tech/auto/">英製雙層電巴投入服務，九巴：成本貴柴油巴逾半冀能獲政府資助</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
